## Limitations & Future Work

- Style may lean stereotypical or repetitive  
- Mislabels on out-of-distribution images  
- Better multimodal models (e.g. GPT‑4V) could improve quality  
- Add user controls (“less slang”, “longer caption”)  
- UI gallery for caption suggestions and edits  

---

## Why this Project

The goal is to make content creation more fun and accessible. Many creators struggle to come up with trendy, catchy captions — this tool automates that in a style-forward way.

